RESUMO-CV.TEXTO-RESUMO-CV-RH:
Possui mestrado em Ecologia e Biomonitoramento pela Universidade Federal da Bahia - UFBA (2019), ps-graduao em andamento em Docncia no Ensino Superior: Tecnologias Educacionais e Inovao e em Percia e Auditoria Ambiental pela Universidade Cesumar ? Unicesumar. licenciada em Cincias Biolgicas pela Universidade Estadual de Maring ? UEM (2016) com um perodo sanduche atravs do programa do governo federal Cincia sem Fronteiras na James Cook University, Austrlia (2013/14) com nfase em ecologia marinha e conservao.
Atuou como estagiria na rea de Gentica (2010/11), com nfase em Gentica do Desenvolvimento, onde desenvolveu trabalhos de iniciao cientfica, no HUEM (Herbrio da Universidade Estadual de Maring) (2012), no Programa Institucional de Bolsa de Iniciao Docncia ? PIBID de Biologia pela Universidade Estadual de Maring ? UEM (2012/13), como educadora ambiental pela Prefeitura de Maring, PR (2013), como pesquisadora estagiria no Projeto Conservao Recifal na unidade de conservao marinha APA dos Corais (Tamandar - PE) (2015) e como tutora EAD no Ensino Superior pela Universidade Cesumar ? Unicesumar (2019/20). Atualmente, professora conteudista no Curso de Pedagogia (EAD) na Unio de Faculdades Metropolitanas de Maring (Centro Universitrio Unifamma) na disciplina de Fundamentos e Metodologia do Ensino de Cincias e atua com pesquisa na rea de impactos antrpicos em recifes de corais.
Possui cursos de mergulho bsico (PADI) e avanado (NAUII).
Tem experincia nas reas de Ensino de Cincias, Biologia e Oceanografia Biolgica, Educao ambiental, Ensino EAD e Ecologia Marinha, Peixes Recifais e Hidrocorais.
RESUMO-CV.TEXTO-RESUMO-CV-RH-EN:
I have a master's degree in Ecology and Biomonitoring from the Federal University of Bahia - UFBA , Brazil (2019), an ongoing graduate course in Teaching in Higher Education: Educational Technologies and Innovation and in Environmental Expertise and Auditing from the Universidade Cesumar - Unicesumar, Brazil. Also, I am a bachelor in Biological Sciences from the State University of Maring - UEM, Brazil (2016) with an exchange period through the federal government's program entitled Science without Borders at James Cook University, Australia (2013/14) with emphasis on marine ecology and conservation.
I worked as an intern in a ​​Genetics laboratory (2010/11), with an emphasis on Developmental Genetics, where I developed scientific initiation studies at HUEM (Herbarium of the State University of Maring), Brazil (2012), in the Institutional Scholarship Program for Initiation to Teaching - PIBID of Biology by the State University of Maring - UEM, Brazil (2012/13), as an environmental educator by the City Hall of Maring, PR, Brazil (2013), as an intern researcher in the Reef Conservation Project at the marine protected area APA dos Corais (Tamandar - PE), Brazil (2015) and as a distance learning tutor in Higher Education at Cesumar University - Unicesumar, Brazil (2019/20). Currently, I am a content teacher in the Pedagogy Course (EAD) at the Union of Faculdades Metropolitanas de Maring (Centro Universitrio Unifamma), Brazil, for the Fundamentals and Methodology of Science Education subject and work with scientific research in ​​anthropogenic impacts on coral reefs.
I have basic diving (PADI) and advanced (NAUII) diving courses.
I have experience experience in the areas of Science Education, Biology and Biological Oceanography, Environmental Education, Distance Education, Marine Ecology, Coral Reef Ecology, Reef Fish and Hydrocorals.
